001package org.galaxyproject.gxformat2.v19_09;
002
003import org.galaxyproject.gxformat2.v19_09.utils.ValidationException;
004
005public enum PrimitiveType {
006  NULL("null"),
007  BOOLEAN("boolean"),
008  INT("int"),
009  LONG("long"),
010  FLOAT("float"),
011  DOUBLE("double"),
012  STRING("string");
013
014  private static String[] symbols =
015      new String[] {"null", "boolean", "int", "long", "float", "double", "string"};
016  private String docVal;
017
018  private PrimitiveType(final String docVal) {
019    this.docVal = docVal;
020  }
021
022  public static PrimitiveType fromDocumentVal(final String docVal) {
023    for (final PrimitiveType val : PrimitiveType.values()) {
024      if (val.docVal.equals(docVal)) {
025        return val;
026      }
027    }
028    throw new ValidationException(
029        String.format("Expected one of %s", PrimitiveType.symbols, docVal));
030  }
031}
